<section id="userguide-requirements">
  <title>Requirements</title>
    <para>
      The initial default installation of Inca has the following 
      requirements:
    </para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>JDK or JRE 1.4.2_09 or greater</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Perl 5.8.6 or greater</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>OpenSSL-0.9.6[jkl] or OpenSSL-0.9.7b or greater</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>GNU tar (i.e., no limit on filename length)</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    <para>
      For each resource Inca will be monitoring, the following is
      required:
    </para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Perl 5.8.x or greater</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>OpenSSL-0.9.6[jkl] or OpenSSL-0.9.7b or greater</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>GNU tar (i.e., no limit on filename length)</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
</section>
